parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery switches can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power brakes and power steering, which can result in accidents, injuries, and stranded vehicles.
symptoms: The engine stops suddenly
loss of power brakes
loss of power steering
inability to turn off the engine battery
violent stops
injuries from falling against the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the auxiliary batteries can cause electrical system malfunctions, leading to inconvenience, discomfort, and potential safety risks.
symptoms: Auxiliary batteries fail repeatedly
electrical system malfunctions.
